name: Rights, powers, supplemental
text: §201G-80   [Section effective July 1, 2006.  For section effective until June 30, 2006, see above.]  The rights or powers conferred upon the administration by this subpart shall be in addition and supplemental to the rights or powers conferred upon the administration by any other law. [L 1997, c 350, pt of §2; am L 2005, c 196, §26(a)]
